** color boxes   
 
   #+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
   /----\ /----\
   |c33F| |cC02|
   |    | |    |
   \----/ \----/
 
   /----\ /----\
   |c1FF| |c1AB|
   |    | |    |
   \----/ \----/
   #+END_EXAMPLE
  
   #+begin_src ditaa :file ../img/2015/2015-12-16-180328-colorbox.png
   /----\ /----\
   |c33F| |cC02|
   |    | |    |
   \----/ \----/
 
   /----\ /----\
   |c1FF| |c1AB|
   |    | |    |
   \----/ \----/
   #+end_src
 
   #+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
   /-------------+-------------\
   |cRED RED     |cBLU BLU     |
   +-------------+-------------+
   |cGRE GRE     |cPNK PNK     |
   +-------------+-------------+
   |cBLK BLK     |cYEL YEL     |
   \-------------+-------------/
   #+END_EXAMPLE

   #+begin_src ditaa :file ../img/2015/2015-12-16-180338-colormap.png
   /-------------+-------------\
   |cRED RED     |cBLU BLU     |
   +-------------+-------------+
   |cGRE GRE     |cPNK PNK     |
   +-------------+-------------+
   |cBLK BLK     |cYEL YEL     |
   \-------------+-------------/
   #+end_src

   #+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
   +---+-----+   +----------+
   | cBLU    |   | {io}     |
   | Ext-Foo |   |  S-ATA   |
   |   +-----+   |   cFEA   | 
   |   |cPNK |   +----------+
   |   | Foo |   
   +---+-----+
   #+END_EXAMPLE

   #+begin_src ditaa :file ../img/2015/2015-12-16-180254-color-boxes.png
   +---+-----+   +----------+
   | cBLU    |   | {io}     |
   | Ext-Foo |   |  S-ATA   |
   |   +-----+   |   cFEA   | 
   |   |cPNK |   +----------+
   |   | Foo |   
   +---+-----+
   #+END_SRC

   #+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
   /-----------------\
   | Things to do    |
   | cGRE            |
   | o Cut the grass |
   | o Buy jam       |
   | o Fix car       |
   | o Make website  |
   \-----------------/
   #+END_EXAMPLE

   #+begin_src ditaa :file ../img/2015/2015-12-16-180405-things-to-do.png
   /-----------------\
   | Things to do    |
   | cGRE            |
   | o Cut the grass |
   | o Buy jam       |
   | o Fix car       |
   | o Make website  |
   \-----------------/
   #+end_src

   #+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
   /-------------+-------------\
   |cRED RED     |cBLU BLU     |
   +-------------+-------------+
   |cGRE GRE     |cPNK PNK     |
   +-------------+-------------+
   |cAAA               AAA     |
   +-------------+-------------+
   |cCCC               CCC     |
   +-------------+-------------+
   |cBLK BLK     |cYEL YEL     |
   \-------------+-------------/  
   #+END_EXAMPLE

